{"tid":39953,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[睡眠台]有無爸絲都有半夜扎醒呢個煩惱？","createTime":"2016-12-15T01:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T01:22:59.000Z","uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"453fe396ec71499a8f1d7fff4629a2cbabfec032","tid":39953,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:10:44.000Z","msg":"我平時十一點幾就上床瞓，都唔會話好難入睡，但係就一星期起碼有三、四日瞓到一點至四點呢段時間就醒左醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然好快會瞓返著但係始終瞓得唔夠爽皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無野可以改善呢個情況？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c24fb4515867b91f2d42290f2b3aef0df11d2787","tid":39953,"uid":18249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:11:41.000Z","msg":"平時三四點會起一起身去廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50a0ef2246514d4bac8f5d5be372336df12807fb","tid":39953,"uid":18794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:12:27.000Z","msg":"一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ee915d120169b13ddd556771d01ff3c8a7b83e","tid":39953,"uid":55679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:13:47.000Z","msg":"唔係半夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5點幾訓 9點幾醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0610beddaa15829a4ce5ac5fb986a997cece28d5","tid":39953,"uid":5086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:18:31.000Z","msg":"我都會<br />\n近牌睇中醫 改善左"},{"pid":"768097e33d64c8d2f7de4ddfad31ef6ca3aae1b0","tid":39953,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲好易俾人嘈醒"},{"pid":"e7703391979ec062db611c8b13c399f57b6b1dea","tid":39953,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:20:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都會<br />\n近牌睇中醫 改善左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我又未至於嚴重到要睇醫生，但係想知有無野食下做下可以改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d494e4ed64a728ed486c42afe868bdb9ba9c101e","tid":39953,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:21:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係半夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n5點幾訓 9點幾醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你係似遲瞓再俾個太陽/出面嘈醒"},{"pid":"793c0ac0ec67853e2f68d765dc876ac3149c6caa","tid":39953,"uid":620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:28:37.000Z","msg":"工作壓力太大？<br />\n我有段時間都係咁，無論幾點訓都會大約五點幾醒<br />\n之後成個腦係咁諗返工d野，訓唔返"},{"pid":"1ad66e351e99a30b1b94706972bf0c15a7a119e6","tid":39953,"uid":48830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:30:21.000Z","msg":"以前有一排十二點幾一點瞓 都係唔夠5點就醒左<br />\n不過逐漸好左"},{"pid":"845ae096ae80621115fe7e5f9167b2227cde7bb2","tid":39953,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T01:57:34.000Z","msg":"一時時，通常都有發夢，睡眠品質差<br />\n過幾日太攰一覺訓到天光"},{"pid":"a2b1079dee255bff5a95d648cd3b109e5127a605","tid":39953,"uid":61542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:10:30.000Z","msg":"搵晚通頂 第二晚你就會訓到昏迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1fc20299d2ded6b289838ea57c99e3bc7243450","tid":39953,"uid":35749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:16:44.000Z","msg":"我都係 就算好夜瞓或者攰到仆哂街 <br />\n都係3 4點醒一醒<br />\n<br />\n除非3點先瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁就8點起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57ceb85a0b518bcc2ce5a67ebfa04cf4498fa99","tid":39953,"uid":18650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:17:54.000Z","msg":"近排成日訓到半路要起身飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df257ee4b0d4031a29488bc04e698f065b4a18b","tid":39953,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:39:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>工作壓力太大？<br />\n我有段時間都係咁，無論幾點訓都會大約五點幾醒<br />\n之後成個腦係咁諗返工d野，訓唔返</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該唔係，做野無乜壓力，<br />\n通常我係發發下夢就醒左，以前發完夢開眼係天光，但係宜家就半夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7477666e27718bdbc0af91d149c489d9f6d3db1","tid":39953,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T02:39:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前有一排十二點幾一點瞓 都係唔夠5點就醒左<br />\n不過逐漸好左</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點樣好翻？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d07055333095ef917657150df820ffa7105c6ccb","tid":39953,"uid":3206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:18:48.000Z","msg":"我又醒撚左喇屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84766d8d097e379309e77d559212dd5884b5b0b4","tid":39953,"uid":25945,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:22:47.000Z","msg":"試下飲下雞精"},{"pid":"0f1eabf66e60d6ae6f4a56dd88513076d6632ebc","tid":39953,"uid":51758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:27:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4ac74df5a5e57186d24ca42f8fa418034e275077","tid":39953,"uid":34427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T17:51:42.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"78eefb58cf7cdf08e67f4197ed7cfb3521f38323","tid":39953,"uid":21156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T20:10:24.000Z","msg":"正常較左鬧鐘4點，但哩排成日2、3點扎醒&hellip;"},{"pid":"fa19c97915cdf26a17233a42fefbe3e9c4de9c10","tid":39953,"uid":12893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T20:26:39.000Z","msg":"呢兩日五點半先訓得着 七點半被屋企人起身啲聲嚇醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前就試過個幾鐘醒一次，係折磨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6ea98b896a0ac6028bbb7f7bc1c69968b3624ff","tid":39953,"uid":6062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T22:57:11.000Z","msg":"近排十一二點訓成日五點零鐘就扎醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都想知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18f010566066df19b7c1bf4f69a818bf369c4248","tid":39953,"uid":3399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T23:32:05.000Z","msg":"十點幾十一點瞓，點幾兩點就會醒，係覺得已經瞓咗好耐然後就仆街瞓過龍既感覺，一望個鐘，屌兩點都未夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f1431de2a74a06685cffe74474fe29cc09a9e51","tid":39953,"uid":17616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T00:28:17.000Z","msg":"其實大家係咪啲好準時嘅人？成日擔心遲到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}